### L3 — Roaming: Export a session into a portable signed token
### SPEC §8.3
### Use case: user finished planning on their laptop, wants to continue on mobile.
### The token can be shared via QR code, push notification, or any channel.

POST /v1/sbp/sessions/a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890/export HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <your-api-key>

{
  "ttl_seconds": 86400,
  "label": "Tokyo trip planning — continue on mobile"
}

